🏅 How to Add Your Credly Badge

You can easily showcase your certification badges from Credly on your GitHub profile.
	1.	Go to your badge on Credly.
	2.	Click on Share and copy the public URL of your badge.
	3.	Replace the link and image in the code below with your own badge URL and image:

  <a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/22336acd-57f2-4d1e-a3a7-af96f007ce8d/linked_in?t=sqdowx">
    <img alt="AWS Cloud Practitioner Badge" width="160px" src="https://images.credly.com/images/00634f82-b07f-4bbd-a6bb-53de397fc3a6/image.png"/> 
</a>

👉 Just replace the link and image with yours. That’s it!
